@startuml
title Gestion des certifications

actor Visiteur as V
actor Proprietaire as Auth
boundary Front as F
control API as API
database BD as BD

== Consultation (publique) ==
V -> F: Navigation page profil
F -> API: GET /api/certifications
note right: Accès libre
API -> BD: SELECT * FROM certifications ORDER BY ordre, date_obtention DESC
BD --> API: Liste des certifications
API --> F: JSON [{titre, organisme, date_obtention, ...}]
F --> V: Affichage certifications

== Gestion (authentifié) ==
Auth -> F: Dashboard certifications
F -> API: GET /api/certifications
note right: Proprietaire uniquement
API -> BD: SELECT ...
BD --> API: Liste complète
API --> F: JSON
F --> Auth: Formulaire de gestion

Auth -> F: Ajouter une certification
F -> API: POST /api/certifications {titre, organisme, ...}
note right: Auth requis (Bearer token)
API -> BD: INSERT INTO certifications
BD --> API: Nouvelle certification
API --> F: 201 Created
F --> Auth: Confirmation

Auth -> F: Modifier une certification
F -> API: PUT /api/certifications/{id} {titre, ...}
API -> BD: UPDATE certifications
BD --> API: Certification modifiée
API --> F: 200 OK
F --> Auth: Confirmation

Auth -> F: Supprimer une certification
F -> API: DELETE /api/certifications/{id}
API -> BD: DELETE FROM certifications
BD --> API: OK
API --> F: 204 No Content
F --> Auth: Confirmation
@enduml
